            <h5><b>Q: </b>How are missionaries called?</h5>
            <h5><b>A: </b>Every missionary who is called and assigned or reassigned to a particular mission is called by revelation through the Lord's servants, the prophets. A member of the Quorum of the Twelve assigns prospective missionaries to one of more than three hundred missions of the Church.</h5>
            <form>
